<br />\n既然連儂牆咁重要，我地又點能夠次次都等何君妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出來打飛機先做野呢？929有人搞左個光復港島區連儂牆既活動，咁我就覺得好撚掂既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，哩單野都無理由只得一日同一個地區，所以我係到諗，會唔會<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每個月十八區都搞個「全民光復連儂牆」</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？  <br />\n<br />\n活動形式未知，我暫時係諗住<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">每個月既第二個星期日</span></span></strong>，每人個日都要自備<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十張文宣痴牆[/size=5]</span>；勇武哩個時間就可以落區幫下手[b][size=6]<span style=\"color: green;\">睇哨</span></span></strong>，正如我上面咁講，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">製造機會俾勇武和理傾下計，</span></strong>凝聚返大家一起。歡迎樓下俾意見！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"自PUSH"},{"pid":"381f22e043a7eb3dbd40554b8b27ef44c454a8c0","tid":1602311,"uid":328032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"自PUSH"},{"pid":"6c74505ee59649693c117b46e7ed57f042c3d367","tid":1602311,"uid":328032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"2747317258ef456faa7d669c3b8797809b39813e","tid":1602311,"uid":328032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:16:01.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"cf3b4e8d67dcb5b4171b9a1228f93deb7212a7a5","tid":1602311,"uid":328032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:53:49.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"b0f2d95247d1e4d4a2c4e9a224d80a20d8525fdb","tid":1602311,"uid":328032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:36:23.000Z","msg":"自push"}]}